import React, { useContext, useState } from 'react' import './Navbar.css' import { assets } from '../assets/assets' import {Link} from 'react-router-dom' const Navbar = ({setLogin}) => { const [menu,setMenu]=useState("menu"); const{getTotal}=useContext() return (
    setMenu("home")} className={menu==="home"?"active":""}>Home setMenu("menu")} className={menu==="menu"?"active":""}>Menu setMenu("contact-us")} className={menu==="contact-us"?"active":""}>Contact Us
) } export default Navbar
